description: The Book Brothers brand is bursting with new trucks, bringing them all to the streets of LA, and serving up some of the best gourmet Chinese cuisine you may ever eat.Their entrees include Sauteed Shredded Pork with an awesome assortment of sauces, as well as Spare Ribs, Chicken, and Shrimp. You’ll also find a few tasty kinds of Noodles and Sides, too!For some beautifully delicious food, be sure to seek out a Book Brothers Truck near you!
name: Book Brothers
